description: Gaming Corps AB is a small, global developer focusing on Gaming, iGaming and Interactive Entertainment. The company is headquartered in Uppsala, Uppsala and currently employs 14 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2015-06-04. The company specializes in AAA titles, personal computer (PC)/ Steam, mobile, and gambling platforms. The company develops and markers casino applications and mobile games. Its portfolio includes: AIR, a game based on the film with the same title, as well as Riddick: The Merck Files and Kill the Dot, mobile games available for iOS and Android operating systems, among others. The firm operates Visual Dreams AB as a wholly owned subsidiary.
name: Gaming Corps AB
